&lt;h3&gt;Network/Looking Glass&lt;/h3&gt;
You can test the performance of our locations before ordering using our Looking Glass, they can be accessed via the pinmarks on our &lt;a href="https://quadhost.net/locations/?&amp;utm_source=lowendtalk&amp;utm_medium=offer-post&amp;utm_content=locations&amp;utm_campaign=15-dec-15"&gt;locations page&lt;/a&gt;.

&lt;h3&gt;Support&lt;/h3&gt;
Services are unmanaged however our UK based support team is on hand 24/7 via telephone and the ticket desk should a hardware or network issue need resolving.
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Addons/Extras&lt;/h3&gt;
Addon pricing varies by location, however we can accommodate larger bandwidth requests, additional IP's (subject to justification) and additional cores/resources; for more information contact us. /64 blocks of IPv6 per instance is being rolled out across our EU locations by 2016 (Pending Panel Upgrades).
&lt;br&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Billing/Pricing&lt;/h3&gt;
Initial purchases may be manually reviewed prior to provisioning, otherwise automated; (&amp;lt;30s typically). All prices exclude VAT. We invoice in GBP.
Residents in the EU will be charged MOSS, if you have a EU VAT ID then your charge will be removed. Prices meet $7/m &gt; £ requirements as of 01:41UTC 15/12/2015. PayPal &amp;  BitCoin are enabled for these product ranges.

